	<item>
		<title>Style Guide: How to Wear Gold Accessories</title>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>Gold accessories can elevate any outfit, but knowing how to style them is key. Our stylists share their top tips for incorporating gold into your daily wardrobe.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

		<!-- wp:heading {"level":3,"style":{"color":{"text":"#c9a96e"}}} -->
		<h3 class="wp-block-heading" style="color:#c9a96e">Less Is More</h3>
		<!-- /wp:heading -->

		<!-- wp:paragraph -->
		<p>Start with one statement piece and build around it. A gold chain or cuff bracelet can transform a simple white shirt into an elegant ensemble.</p>
		<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
		<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[Stylist tips for incorporating gold accessories into your daily wardrobe — from statement pieces to subtle accents.]]></excerpt:encoded>
		<wp:post_type>post</wp:post_type>
		<wp:post_name>gold-accessories-guide</wp:post_name>
